flowchart TD
    RecoveryStart([Choose recovery after sign-in failure]) --> FailureInput[Submit username and allow-listed failure code]
    FailureInput --> StartTransaction[Create short-lived Recovery Transaction]
    StartTransaction --> ComputePolicy[Compute complete allowed Recovery Actions]
    ComputePolicy --> AnotherPasskey{Another passkey path allowed?}
    AnotherPasskey -- Yes --> PreferAuthentication[Recommend normal Authentication first]
    AnotherPasskey -- No --> FactorConfigured{Recovery Code configured?}
    FactorConfigured -- No --> NoSelfService[Explain self-service is unavailable]
    FactorConfigured -- Yes --> CollectDescription[Collect bounded non-secret description]
    CollectDescription --> SecretLike{Secret-like content detected?}
    SecretLike -- Yes --> RejectSecret[Do not send; direct to Security Authorization]
    SecretLike -- No --> CallModel[Call GPT-5.6 with policy projection]
    CallModel --> ModelValid{Schema and semantic output valid?}
    ModelValid -- No --> DeterministicFallback[Use deterministic explanation]
    ModelValid -- Yes --> IntersectActions[Intersect output with server action set]
    IntersectActions --> ShowGuidance[Show diagnosis and explicit security boundary]
    DeterministicFallback --> ShowGuidance
    RejectSecret --> ShowGuidance
    PreferAuthentication --> ShowGuidance
    NoSelfService --> TerminalNoBypass([Stop without authorization])
    ShowGuidance --> FactorRequired([Proceed only to a server-approved action])
